Package cop3330.models

package cop3330.models
Contains the core domain model classes representing entities in the system.

This package includes the following primary classes:

  • Student — Abstract base class for student entities.
  • Course — Represents a course with details such as code, title, and credit hours.
  • GraduateStudent — Concrete subclass of Student representing graduate students.
  • UndergraduateStudent — Concrete subclass of Student representing undergraduate students.

These classes encapsulate the key business entities and their behaviors within the application.
